                    +--net.sourceforge.gjtapi.raw.remote.RemoteListenerImpl
public class RemoteListenerImpl
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements RemoteListener

This is a wrapper class for a RawListener that lets the RawListener receive remote updates. On the Framework side, this translates RemoteListener skeleton calls to be passed on to the real RawListener. Creation date: (2000-02-17 13:09:32)
